(0)
Parsons Boulevard, east side, north of Highland Ave., showing the Normal School of Jamaica, now known as the Teachers Training
school.
About 1910.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
Another view; note the addition of the clock in the apex of the building and the growth attain by the trees in the
front of the school.
March 23,1927.
P. L. Sperr.
